%H A281701 A. van den Brandhof, J. Guichelaar, and A. Jaspers, <a href="http://www.maa.org/press/ebooks/half-a-century-of-pythagoras-magazine">Half a Century of Pythagoras Magazine</a>, MAA, 2015, 225
